title: My online match history isn't working. Just a rectangle with nothing in it
body: How can I contact Riot to fix this issue? None of my browsers work and I've tried almost everything. I assume that this is a problem with my account at this point. I need to view my match history from early last year for items/spells/mast that I was using for champs. Thanks a lot!

replies.body: This is currently being looked into, but I have no additional eta or information on the external match history site.  You might be able to workaround this by resetting your [cache and cookies](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752694-Clearing-Browser-History-and-Cookies), and a force refresh by pressing Ctrl+Shift+R.  I hope that helps!
